Sentencas: In the present work, the ohmic resistance of an integrated planar-SOFC (IP-SOFC) has been evaluated by developing a model whose equations have been solved numerically through an FEM method.
Titulo: FEM model of the ohmic resistance of IP-SOFCs

Sentencas: The model allows to estimate the distribution of voltage and current density in the cell.
Titulo: FEM model of the ohmic resistance of IP-SOFCs

Sentencas: A comparison between simulated and experimental data of area specific resistance is reported, which shows satisfactory agreement.
Titulo: FEM model of the ohmic resistance of IP-SOFCs

Sentencas: The mathematical model has also been used to carry out some parametric studies for optimisation purposes.
Titulo: FEM model of the ohmic resistance of IP-SOFCs

Sentencas: Indeed, a reduction in cell pitch length and an increase in electrode thickness are predicted to lead to a reduction in ohmic losses in IP-SOFCs.
Titulo: FEM model of the ohmic resistance of IP-SOFCs
